         <div type="translation">
            <ab>3. NN wa]s priest of; [Sarapis and Peteph]res of Apis; NN ga]ve birth to Pete[phres...  who is] called; ... NN gave bir]th to Jannes [and Jambres the t]wo sons of his; [- - -] Jannes and Jambres were magicians ..]</ab>
